{"type": "article", "id": 21978, "title": "自行车挂墙工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122251y3V8L2GFmsxJKZBn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这些挂在墙上的木头工具都是帮助将自行车挂在墙上的，Lignum Bike Company 从自行车结构的各个部位出发，开发了一系列工具，或者是拖出车架或座杆的柜子，或者是一根安放轮胎的横木，而用皮条将脚踏板夹住，一些柜子还有放配件的功能。横挂在墙上的自行车有一份工业美感，这组设计产自加拿大，<a href=\"https://lignumbike.com/get-it-on-the-wall-shop-now/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122250H3T7MFn2rzsicwDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122250rnwdplOJTDmBUgb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122250sK7al24qDNkvY9Up.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122251nAlZFmUExMc9hWTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}